data.name: SqlCommand45.CommandText
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT qs2.tblSelListEntries.ID AS IDSelListChapter, qs2.getAllUsersWithRoles.ID AS IDObject, qs2.tblSelListEntriesObj.IDClassification FROM qs2.tblSelListGroup AS tblSelListGroup_1 INNER JOIN qs2.tblSelListEntries AS tblSelListEntries_1 ON tblSelListGroup_1.ID = tblSelListEntries_1.IDGroup INNER JOIN qs2.tblSelListGroup INNER JOIN qs2.tblSelListEntries ON qs2.tblSelListGroup.ID = qs2.tblSelListEntries.IDGroup INNER JOIN qs2.tblSelListEntriesObj ON qs2.tblSelListEntries.ID = qs2.tblSelListEntriesObj.IDSelListEntry ON tblSelListEntries_1.ID = qs2.tblSelListEntriesObj.IDSelListEntrySublist INNER JOIN qs2.getAllUsersWithRoles ON tblSelListEntries_1.ID = qs2.getAllUsersWithRoles.IDSelListEntry WHERE (qs2.tblSelListGroup.IDGroupStr IN ('Chapters0', 'Chapters1', 'ProcGrp0', 'ProcGrp1')) AND (tblSelListGroup_1.IDGroupStr = 'Roles') AND (qs2.tblSelListEntriesObj.IDClassification <> '')
